Ahh! How... adorable...! Please become my...
fianc...

Even if we can pass through the impregnable Gate
of Tenma, I wonder if there's a way to cross that
inferno zone...

I ended up going on an incredibly difficult
quest... What should I do...
I have to accept quests that suit me, don't I?

It was a mistake to try to act all cool and say,
Of course, I can handle something like this! just
because my comrades said so...

I'll spare you the details, but to put it simply,
I'll probably die...

Hey... I'm begging you... Before I die, I just
want to have sex with a cute person like you, even
just once!
I can't help it (Requires a lewdness level of 300 or higher)en(v[261]>=300)
Ugh... I guess there's no helping it...
In exchange, make sure you come back alive, okay?

Keel: Ugh... It was so amazing... I will
definitely come back alive... to see you...!!!
Thank you, Konoha!
Oh no... Did you die before going on the quest?

Ugh... It was so amazing... I will definitely come
back alive... to see you...!!! Thank you, Konoha!
What are you saying! It's obviously impossible!!!

Yeah... Uh-huh, sorry for asking something
weird...

I feel like I'm going crazy... Well... I'll go on
the quest with the intention of dying...
